 日，小米汽车官方正式宣布演员、导演舒淇出任小米汽车品牌代言人，这是继 3 月 17 日官宣苏炳添后，小米汽车在三天内公布的第二位品牌代言人。 小米汽车官方发文称：「从镜头前，到镜头后。她，始终以从容的姿态，保持自己的节奏，不断走向新的世界。今天，她又解锁了一个新角色，小米汽车品牌代言人。不仅因为，她非常喜爱第一代 SU7 的乘坐体验。更因为，我们都拥有，从容驾驭每一程的底气。」 小米汽车官宣舒淇为第二位代言人，新一代 SU7 今晚正式上市 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d863e532ae3d823f6b299fc8c6c6cd57.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017891290054943068"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI24f28Kaf+OghEAMaCTExODgxMjMxMiCWm+3NBjAAOMACQAZyEzIwMTc4OTEyOTAwNTQ5NDMwNjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1773972472.541674", "card_id": "Q_1908833817701095067", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么短剧明明剧情也不咋地，观众却那么宽容？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我看好几部短剧，红果的，包括比较大热的乖乖女，但是我觉质量真的很一般，配角演技也很浮夸，几乎就是看二人转，而且短剧其实水分也很大，没少注水，为啥观众那么宽容，全是夸短剧的。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-4a5959e0d6470faea399e90beaf23705_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "120 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1908833817701095067"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI24f28Kaf+OghEAMaCTExNTA0OTY0MiDmm7rBBjAAOIMBQAdyEzE5MDg4MzM4MTc3MDEwOTUwNjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1773972472.543342", "card_id": "Q_2017223907044718478", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c8